ref":"Josh.24.3","text":"And I took your father Abraham from the other side of the flood, and led him throughout all the land of Canaan, and multiplied his seed, and gave him Isaac.","year":-1427},{"id":"recDvhkJ1ljDe9iTt","ref":"Josh.24.4","text":"And I gave unto Isaac Jacob and Esau: and I gave unto Esau mount Seir, to possess it; but Jacob and his children went down into Egypt.","year":-1427},{"id":"rece9opjyXqnrDRrN","ref":"Josh.24.5","text":"I sent Moses also and Aaron, and I plagued Egypt, according to that which I did among them: and afterward I brought you out.","year":-1427},{"id":"rec6P4nIPnO7Skl3Y","ref":"Josh.24.6","text":"And I brought your fathers out of Egypt: and ye came unto the sea; and the Egyptians pursued after your fathers with chariots and horsemen unto the Red sea.","year":-1427},{"id":"recUz516TkcNjbAxu","ref":"Josh.24.7","text":"And when they cried unto the LORD, he put darkness between you and the Egyptians, and brought the sea upon them, and covered them; and your eyes have seen what I have done in Egypt: and ye dwelt in the wilderness a long season.","year":-1427},{"id":"reckoQ7XL5dWyvH8r","ref":"Josh.24.8","text":"And I brought you into the land of the Amorites, which dwelt on the other side Jordan; and they fought with you: and I gave them into your hand, that ye might possess their land; and I destroyed them from before you.","year":-1427}]}
